  Second-4100000000 <BR>Depth: infinity <BR>Content-Type: text/xml;=20
  charset=3D"utf-8" <BR>Content-Length: xxxx <BR>Authorization: Digest=20
  username=3D"ejw", <BR>realm=3D"ejw@webdav.sb.aol.com", nonce=3D"...",=20
  <BR>uri=3D"/workspace/webdav/proposal.doc", <BR>response=3D"...", =
